parameters.name: MET
parameters.description: Mission Elapsed Time at the end of the accumulation.

parameters.name: DATA_QUALITY
parameters.description:
Data quality flag.
   =0 Good Data, =1 Undefined Bad Data,
   =2 Hot Pixel, =4 Scan Hard Limit Exceeded,
   =8 SEP, =16 Start Rate Anomaly,
   =32 Bad WSZ, 128 Instrument Off,
   =32768 Flag Value is Manually Defined.

parameters.name: FIPS_SCANTYPE
parameters.description:
Indicates the FIPS Scan Mode. Tables referenced here 
   are one of the eight E/q stepping tables loaded into the instrument. 
   See the EPPS CDR SIS in the EPPS Document Archive Volume for details.
   =0 Normal Scan, =1 High Temp Scan, =2 Burst Scan, =3 Test Scan, 
   =4 Table 4, =5 Table 5, =6 Table 6, =7 Table 7.
